{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/EN1.png?t=1738098340\" /><br><br>Live an interstellar voyage through space and time, from youth to old age, from planet Earth to the edge of the galaxy, from complete loneliness to being reunited with your loved ones. You are a forgotten child who will travel across the real star systems of our galaxy looking for other space refugees like you, to live in peace.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/Leaving.gif?t=1738098340\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/Starpath.gif?t=1738098340\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/EN3.png?t=1738098340\" /><br><br>Track the signals of huge spaceships that the humans have used to leave Earth. However outer space is not merciful. If you reach a Mothership that didn't survive, salvage its core and use its fuel to venture searching deeper into space.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/Desert.gif?t=1738098340\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/Core.gif?t=1738098340\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/EN4.png?t=1738098340\" /><br><br>Use your compass radar and your sense of observation to find your own way to the cores across asteroids fields, exotic planets and Motherships' wrecks. You have at your disposal the equipment to endure hazardous environments and to open new shortcuts in your path. Learn and adapt to different gravities, natural dangers and even catastrophic events.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/IceRappel.gif?t=1738098340\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/Compass.gif?t=1738098340\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/EN2.png?t=1738098340\" /><br><br>Experience the calm and the thrill of zero gravity. Learn to navigate in weightlessness with a pair of rocket space boots, where every impulse counts, or take a break and drift, watching the universe pass by from the safety of your ship's cupola.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/Rocket.gif?t=1738098340\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/Cupola.gif?t=1738098340\" /><br><br><br><br>I hope you'll enjoy it :)<br>Carlos<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/AddToYourWishlist.jpg?t=1738098340\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738098340","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/page.bg.jpg?t=1738098340","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738098340","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738098340","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/EN1.png?t=17